T02D2316:261a-1: y'a na w'aka pra d'i la n'a ma /
T02D2316:261a-3: theg pa gsung gi sgron ma zhes bya ba /
T02D2316:261a-4: 'jam dpal smra ba'i seng ge la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2316:261a-5: khams gsum sems can ma lus kun //
T02D2316:261a-6: ma rig mun pas 'thibs pa la //
T02D2316:261a-7: ston pa bcom ldan sh'aka thub kyis //
T02D2316:261a-8: gsung gi sgron ma 'di bstan pas //
T02D2316:261a-9: dam chos rim pa gsum du gsungs //
T02D2316:261a-10: rgyas par gsungs dang 'bring du bshad //
T02D2316:261a-11: bsdus pa'i don du bstan pa'o //
T02D2316:261a-12: de la rgyas par gsungs pa ni //
T02D2316:261a-13: dug gsum nyon mongs cha mnyam pa'i //
T02D2316:261a-14: gnyen po brgyad khri bzhi stong ste //
T02D2316:261a-15: theg pa sna tshogs bstan pa'o //
T02D2316:261a-16: 'bring ni gsung rab bcu gnyis dang //
T02D2316:261a-17: mdo dang dbyangs bsnyad lung bstan dang //
T02D2316:261a-18: tshigs bcad ched brjod gleng gzhi dang //
T02D2316:261a-19: rtogs brjod de byung skyes pa'i rabs //
T02D2316:261a-20: rgyas dang rmad byung gtan la dbab //
T02D2316:261b-0: bsdus pas sde snod @261b gsum dag ste //
T02D2316:261b-1: mdo sde 'dus pa chos mngon no //
T02D2316:261b-2: lta ba gtsor ston mngon pa ste //
T02D2316:261b-3: bsgom pa gtsor ston mdo sde yin //
T02D2316:261b-5: de yang rnam pa gsum yin te //
T02D2316:261b-6: che dang chung dang khyab par ro //
T02D2316:261b-7: dang po lnga ni mdo yin te //
T02D2316:261b-8: de rjes drug ni 'dul ba yin //
T02D2316:261b-9: nangs kyi tha ma mngon pa'o //
T02D2316:261b-10: de ni theg pa chung du'i gzhung //
T02D2316:261b-11: rgyas dang rmad byung mdo yin te //
T02D2316:261b-12: mdo sogs dgu ni 'dul ba la //
T02D2316:261b-13: gtan la dbab pa mngon pa'i sde //
T02D2316:261b-14: de ni theg pa chen po'i gzhung //
T02D2316:261b-15: mdo sogs rim lnga mang yin te //
T02D2316:261b-16: de rjes rnam bzhi 'dul ba la //
T02D2316:261b-17: tha ma gsum ni mngon pa'o //
T02D2316:261b-18: de ni khyad par bla med gzhung //
T02D2316:261b-19: de bzhin sbyor ba shes par bya //
T02D2316:261b-20: khyad par dbang du byas nas ni //
T02D2316:261b-21: mtshan nyid rgyu yi theg pa dang //
T02D2316:261b-23: de gnyis rgyu 'bras khyad par yang //
T02D2316:261b-24: don gcig la yang ma rmongs te //
T02D2316:261b-25: thabs mang dka' ba med pa yis//
T02D2316:261b-26: dbang po rnon pos dbang byas te //
T02D2316:261b-27: pha rol phyin pa'i theg pa pas //
T02D2316:261b-28: sngags kyi theg pa khyad par 'phags //
T02D2316:261b-29: sngags la rgyud sde bzhi ru gsungs //
T02D2316:261b-30: bya ba'i rgyud dang spyod pa'i rgyud //
T02D2316:261b-31: rnal 'byor rgyud dang bla med pa'o //
T02D2316:261b-32: dman pa rnams la bya ba'i rgyud //
T02D2316:261b-33: bya min rnal 'byor de ltag la//
T02D2316:261b-34: rab la rnal 'byor bla med do //
T02D2316:261b-35: yang na mi rigs bzhi las ni //
T02D2316:261b-36: bram ze'i rigs la bya ba'i rgyud //
T02D2316:261b-37: dmangs rigs la ni spyod pa yi //
T02D2316:261b-38: de bzhin rje'u rigs rnal 'byor rgyud //
T02D2316:261b-39: rgyal rigs rnal 'byor bla med do //
T02D2316:261b-40: 'di ni bla med rgyud du grags //
T02D2316:261b-41: rgyud dang thabs dang 'bras bu las//
T02D2316:261b-42: 'di ni thabs kyi rgyud du gsungs //
T02D2316:261b-43: zab cing rgya che'i zhi byed 'di //
T02D2316:261b-44: brgyud pa rnam pa bzhi ru bshad //
T02D2316:261b-45: rigs kyi rgyud dang don gyi rgyud //
T02D2316:261b-46: byin rlabs brgyud dang brda yi brgyud //
T02D2316:261b-47: ma zhugs rnam bzhi shes par bya //
